    // --- Wooden Box / Jaeger (roubles) ---
    // The wooden box accepts everything by default, so use extraExcludedFilters
    // to block specific items or categories (e.g. other storage cases you don't want going inside).
    // Example line for excluding the following cases (in order):
    //   > Gear Box (from this mod), Lucky Scav Junk Box, Items Case, and THICC Items Case:
    //   > "extraExcludedFilters": ["683d0995deed9b8d4f897ec2", "5b7c710788a4506dec015957", "59fb042886f7746c5005a7b2", "5c0a840b86f7742ffa4f2482"],
